<h1>HTML + CSS + JS â†’ Single JS Snippet</h1>

<label>HTML:</label>
<textarea id="htmlInput" placeholder="Paste your HTML here"></textarea>

<label>CSS:</label>
<textarea id="cssInput" placeholder="Paste your CSS here"></textarea>

